  "text": "Amazon Fire TV Cube $90 $140 Save $50 Brand Amazon Operating System Fire OS Downloadable Apps Yes Resolution 4K Ports HDMI, Micro-USB The Amazon Fire TV Cube (3rd Gen) is Amazon's most powerful media streamer. If you have a house powered by Alexa, this is going to be an excellent addition. Grab it now for its lowest price at just $90. If you love having instant access to your favorite movies and TV shows, a streaming device is going to be an absolute must. Not only does it provide a more convenient way to access the best streaming services available, but you're also going to get the best video and audio quality as well. Now, the Amazon Fire TV series is one of the more popular options, providing a wide range of choices for nearly every budget. But if you've been looking to go all out with the best option, the Fire TV Cube is going to be the way to go. The good news is that ahead of Prime Day, we're seeing one of the best discounts on the device, dropping it down to just $90 for a limited time. What's great about the Amazon Fire TV Cube? The Fire TV Cube is a little different from your average streaming product, offering one of the smoothest experiences thanks to its powerful internals. In fact, Amazon boasts that this model is twice as powerful as the brand's Fire TV Stick 4K Max, which is a pretty big deal. You'll gain access to all the top streaming services out there right now, and can even access these shows hands-free using the included remote that can take commands using Amazon Alexa. You can even control other devices plugged into the Fire TV cube as well. Related And while most devices will require you to stream via Wi-Fi, this box gives you the option of using Ethernet. Of course, Wi-Fi is going to be an option with the Fire TV Cube, with excellent connectivity thanks to it featuring Wi-Fi 6E. In addition to all of the above, the Fire TV Cube can act as a smart hub, giving you the convenient power to control all your Alexa-compatible devices. Again, this is the best Amazon streaming device that you can buy, so if you've been thinking about upgrading your current setup, or wanted to dive into the world of streaming head first, this device is going to be for you.",
